# LLM Provider API Keys
# 
# Set at least one provider's API key to enable AI-powered features.
# The system will automatically detect which providers are available.
#
# Priority order: Anthropic → OpenAI → Google → Azure → OpenRouter

# Anthropic (Claude) - Recommended for code tasks
# Get key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# OpenAI (GPT-4)
# Get key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-key-here

# Google (Gemini) - Has free tier
# Get key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIza-your-key-here

# Azure OpenAI
# AZURE_API_KEY=your-key-here
# AZURE_API_BASE=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com/
# AZURE_API_VERSION=2023-05-15

# OpenRouter (Access to many models)
# Get key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-your-key-here

# Optional: IDE Configuration
# IDE_PROJECT_PATH=/path/to/your/project
